| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6763 — Recovery Inhibition (blackshrantac)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 02552528-1109-5b2d-8aa6-840ffdfa0dd8"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
